<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4432001>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 47. Aposphragisma sepilok sp. nov. Male: A–B. palp prolateral view (B: hairs omitted except trichobothria); C. embolus-conductor-complex prolateral view; D. abdomen ventral view. Female: E. abdomen ventral view. Cb, conical bulge; con, conductor; cr, curved ridge; em, embolus; esp, embolic spine; lap, postepigastric lateral apodemes; spp, spermophor; spo, spermophor opening. Scale bars: A–B 100 µm; C 50 µm; D–E 200 µm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4432001/files/figure.png" .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4431999>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 46. Aposphragisma sepilok sp. nov. Male: A. carapace dorsal view; C. prosoma ventral view; E. carapace lateral view; G. carapace front view; H. carapace lateral view. Female: B. carapace dorsal view; D. prosoma ventral view; F. carapace lateral view. Bc, book lung cover; ctg, continuous transverse groove; sr, subterminal widely oval scutal ridge; tlp, tooth-like projection of male chelicerae. Scale bars: A–H 200 µm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4431999/files/figure.png" .

